{"tid":680480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Prestige片庫遭駭　女優自危！傳數百支無碼片外流","createTime":"2018-05-27T08:24:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T08:40:49.000Z","uid":72009,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7449bbbcbb63b5f85e83fb89f1ee9ea6d0e39c68","tid":680480,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:24:15.000Z","msg":"「AV達人」一劍浣春秋今在部落格「playno1」發文，表示一名駭客宣稱自己駭進了片商「蚊香社」(Prestige)的片庫，並拿到數以百計「無碼」的母帶，得手後他聯絡對方將這些片子「買回去」，否則將外流，結果蚊香社完全不理他，讓他氣得上討論區公布手上的名單，還流出其中一位女優「嶋野遥香」的母帶截圖。<br />\n雖然這篇文章已遭到刪除，但那名單看了真的會嚇死人，除了AV界女神級人物彩美旬果(あやみ旬果)和鈴村愛里(鈴村あいり)外，還有像長谷川留衣(長谷川るい)、上原瑞穂、熊倉祥子(熊倉しょうこ)等大牌女優，但一劍浣春秋認為「這個人的手上確實是有些蚊香社沒上馬賽克的母帶，但有沒有他講的那麼多很難講」、「尤其是他只丟一支作品就在兜售其他女優的方式實在蠻詭異的」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180527/1361962\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180527%2F1361962&d=ScJHb5btZNdrEc9xxEec%2FttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=1b0e5689\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180527%2F1361962&h=e506171d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180527/1361962</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180527/640_1e1a82c8ee50ffe24699b2cf6b0c2d1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180527%2F640_1e1a82c8ee50ffe24699b2cf6b0c2d1e.jpg&h=f7764d96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180527/640_d206579bffe3936c72e84062d857d400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180527%2F640_d206579bffe3936c72e84062d857d400.jpg&h=a7370a6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20dfe3cdde99c1105cfd6e972916460bf2280635","tid":680480,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cit